prospects.name: Matthew Christy
prospects.first_line: Impressed Bluestone Lane rolled out Square across 65 locations—are you also simplifying scheduling, time clocks, and compliance for your Northeast cafes? Homebase cuts labor cost and chaos across multi-location hourly teams.
prospects.evidence_quote: Bluestone Lane recently updated its legacy point-of-sale system and rolled out Square’s all-in-one technology platform across its 65 locations.
